description:
// Sean O'Neill - Esoteric Languages
Esoteric programming languages are Turing complete languages, created without the constraints of being 'comprehensible' or 'remotely useful'.

They are instead, creative, weird and beautiful. Join us on a brief tour of the most popular esoteric programming languages, to point and laugh and maybe learn something.

// About Sean
Sean O'Neill is a passionate software engineer who loves to make games in his spare time.
